{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775866617302,"sessionID":"ses_2861a5243ffeYwG9du5NinetXQ","part":{"id":"prt_d79e61a35001gy2pAlw4zWud6Y","messageID":"msg_d79e60cc2001V4olQ35ibS87pJ","sessionID":"ses_2861a5243ffeYwG9du5NinetXQ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_0d5f14bee39848699b00dd3d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型增强\n2: \n3: ## Summary\n4: \n5: 增强 MetadataService 和数据模型，实现完整的元数据生命周期管理和验证功能。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: ### Background\n10: \n11: `AgentMetadata` 和 `MetadataService` 是 CLI 核心的元数据管理组件。当前实现存在以下问题:\n12: 1. `AgentMetadata` 位于 `services` 包，而非 `models` 包\n13: 2. 缺少 `update_metadata` 方法\n14: 3. 缺少语言特定的工作区验证\n15: 4. `MetadataOptions` 缺少 `from_options` 类方法\n16: \n17: ### Goal\n18: \n19: 1. 迁移 AgentMetadata 到 models 包统一管理\n20: 2. 实现完整的 MetadataService CRUD 操作\n21: 3. 添加语言特定验证逻辑\n22: 4. 增强 MetadataOptions\n23: \n24: ### Value\n25: \n26: - **模块化**: 数据模型与业务逻辑分离\n27: - **可维护性**: 统一的模型定义位置\n28: - **完整性**: 完整的元数据生命周期支持\n29: - **可验证性**: 语言特定工作区验证\n30: \n31: ---\n32: \n33: ## Scope\n34: \n35: ### In-Scope\n36: \n37: | Component | Path | Description |\n38: |-----------|------|-------------|\n39: | AgentMetadata | `agentcube/models/agent_models.py` | 新的独立模型文件 |\n40: | MetadataOptions | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | 增强的方法 |\n41: | MetadataService | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | 新增方法 |\n42: | Unit tests | `tests/test_metadata_service.py` | 测试覆盖 |\n43: \n44: ### Out-of-Scope\n45: \n46: - CLI 命令参数变更\n47: - Runtime 类修改\n48: - 数据库持久化\n49: \n50: ---\n51: \n52: ## Impact Analysis\n53: \n54: ### Dependencies\n55: \n56: | Dependency | Purpose | Status |\n57: |------------|---------|--------|\n58: | `pydantic>=2.0.0` | 数据模型验证 | Existing |\n59: | `pyyaml>=6.0` | YAML 序列化 | Existing |\n60: \n61: ### Upstream\n62: \n63: - `cli-toolkit/design.md` — MetadataService 设计\n64: - `cli-toolkit/spec.md` — 元数据需求\n65: \n66: ### Downstream Consumers\n67: \n68: 1. **PackRuntime** — 元数据加载和验证\n69: 2. **BuildRuntime** — 版本管理\n70: 3. **PublishRuntime** — 部署信息\n71: 4. **InvokeRuntime** — 端点信息\n72: \n73: ### Risks\n74: \n75: | Risk | Severity | Mitigation |\n76: |------|----------|------------|\n77: | Import 变更 | Medium | 保持向后兼容导出 |\n78: | 破坏性变更 | High | 添加兼容层 |\n79: \n80: ---\n81: \n82: ## Alternatives Considered\n83: \n84: ### Option 1: 保持现状 (Not Selected)\n85: \n86: 仅添加缺失方法，不移动模型位置。\n87: \n88: **Cons**:\n89: - 模型定义位置不合理\n90: - 不符合设计 spec\n91: \n92: ### Option 2: 完全重构 (Selected)\n93: \n94: 迁移 AgentMetadata 到 models 包，增强 MetadataService。\n95: \n96: **Pros**:\n97: - 符合设计规范\n98: - 模块化更好\n99: - 便于维护\n100: \n101: **Cons**:\n102: - 需要更新多个 import\n103: \n104: ---\n105: \n106: ## Implementation Plan\n107: \n108: ### Phase 1: 模型迁移\n109: - [ ] 创建 `agentcube/models/agent_models.py`\n110: - [ ] 移动 AgentMetadata 到新文件\n111: - [ ] 更新 models/__init__.py 导出\n112: - [ ] 更新 services/metadata_service.py import\n113: \n114: ### Phase 2: MetadataService 增强\n115: - [ ] 实现 `update_metadata` 方法\n116: - [ ] 实现 `_validate_python_workspace` 方法\n117: - [ ] 实现 `_validate_java_workspace` 方法\n118: - [ ] 更新 save_metadata 使用 exclude_none\n119: \n120: ### Phase 3: MetadataOptions 增强\n121: - [ ] 添加 `from_options` 类方法\n122: - [ ] 确保字段默认值一致\n123: \n124: ### Phase 4: 测试\n125: - [ ] 更新现有测试 import\n126: - [ ] 添加新方法测试\n127: \n128: ---\n129: \n130: ## Acceptance Criteria\n131: \n132: ### AgentMetadata 模型\n133: \n134: | ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n135: |----|----------|-----------------|\n136: | AM-001 | 导出路径 | `from agentcube.models import AgentMetadata` 可用 |\n137: | AM-002 | 字段验证 | language 只能是 python/java |\n138: | AM-003 | 字段验证 | port 范围 1-65535 |\n139: | AM-004 | 默认值 | language 默认为 python |\n140: \n141: ### MetadataService\n142: \n143: | ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n144: |----|----------|-----------------|\n145: | MS-001 | load_metadata | 正确加载 agent_metadata.yaml |\n146: | MS-002 | save_metadata | 使用 exclude_none=True |\n147: | MS-003 | update_metadata | 正确合并更新并保存 |\n148: | MS-004 | validate_python | 无 .py 文件时抛出 ValueError |\n149: | MS-005 | validate_java | 无 pom.xml 时抛出 ValueError |\n150: \n151: ### MetadataOptions\n152: \n153: | ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n154: |----|----------|-----------------|\n155: | MO-001 | from_options | 正确从 dict 创建实例 |\n156: \n157: ---\n158: \n159: ## Technical Design\n160: \n161: ### AgentMetadata 模型\n162: \n163: ```python\n164: # agentcube/models/agent_models.py\n165: from pydantic import BaseModel, Field, field_validator\n166: from typing import Optional, Dict, Any\n167: \n168: class AgentMetadata(BaseModel):\n169:     model_config = {\"extra\": \"forbid\"}\n170:     \n171:     agent_name: str = Field(..., description=\"Unique name identifying the agent\")\n172:     description: Optional[str] = Field(default=None, description=\"Human-readable summary\")\n173:     language: str = Field(default=\"python\", description=\"Programming language used\")\n174:     entrypoint: str = Field(..., description=\"Command to launch the agent\")\n175:     port: int = Field(default=8080, description=\"Port exposed by the agent runtime\")\n176:     build_mode: str = Field(default=\"local\", description=\"Build strategy: local or cloud\")\n177:     region: Optional[str] = Field(default=None, description=\"Deployment region\")\n178:     version: Optional[str] = Field(default=None, description=\"Semantic version string\")\n179:     image: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = Field(default=None)\n180:     auth: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = Field(default=None)\n181:     requirements_file: Optional[str] = Field(default=\"requirements.txt\")\n182:     registry_url: Optional[str] = Field(default=\"\")\n183:     registry_username: Optional[str] = Field(default=\"\")\n184:     registry_password: Optional[str] = Field(default=\"\")\n185:     agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n186:     workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n187:     router_url: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n188:     readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n189:     readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = Field(default=None)\n190:     agent_id: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n191:     session_id: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n192:     k8s_deployment: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = Field(default=None)\n193: \n194:     @field_validator(\"language\")\n195:     @classmethod\n196:     def validate_language(cls, v: str) -> str:\n197:         v_lower = v.lower()\n198:         if v_lower not in (\"python\", \"java\"):\n199:             raise ValueError(\"Language must be 'python' or 'java'\")\n200:         return v_lower\n201: \n202:     @field_validator(\"build_mode\")\n203:     @classmethod\n204:     def validate_build_mode(cls, v: str) -> str:\n205:         v_lower = v.lower()\n206:         if v_lower not in (\"local\", \"cloud\"):\n207:             raise ValueError(\"Build mode must be 'local' or 'cloud'\")\n208:         return v_lower\n209: \n210:     @field_validator(\"port\")\n211:     @classmethod\n212:     def validate_port(cls, v: int) -> int:\n213:         if not isinstance(v, int):\n214:             raise ValueError(\"Port must be an integer\")\n215:         if v < 1 or v > 65535:\n216:             raise ValueError(\"Port must be between 1 and 65535\")\n217:         return v\n218: ```\n219: \n220: ### MetadataService 更新\n221: \n222: ```python\n223: # agentcube/services/metadata_service.py\n224: from agentcube.models.agent_models import AgentMetadata\n225: \n226: class MetadataService:\n227:     METADATA_FILES = [\"agent_metadata.yaml\", \"agent.yaml\", \"metadata.yaml\"]\n228: \n229:     @staticmethod\n230:     def load_metadata(workspace_path: str | Path) -> AgentMetadata: ...\n231:     \n232:     @staticmethod\n233:     def save_metadata(workspace_path: str | Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> Path:\n234:         workspace = Path(workspace_path)\n235:         metadata_file = workspace / \"agent_metadata.yaml\"\n236:         \n237:         with open(metadata_file, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n238:             yaml.safe_dump(\n239:                 metadata.model_dump(exclude_none=True), \n240:                 f, \n241:                 default_flow_style=False, \n242:                 sort_keys=False\n243:             )\n244:         return metadata_file\n245: \n246:     @staticmethod\n247:     def update_metadata(workspace_path: str | Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata:\n248:         \"\"\"Load, merge updates, save pattern.\"\"\"\n249:         metadata = MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n250:         updated = metadata.model_copy(update=updates)\n251:         MetadataService.save_metadata(workspace_path, updated)\n252:         return updated\n253: \n254:     @staticmethod\n255:     def validate_workspace(workspace_path: str | Path) -> bool: ...\n256: \n257:     @staticmethod\n258:     def _validate_python_workspace(workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n259:         py_files = list(workspace_path.glob(\"*.py\"))\n260:         if not py_files:\n261:             raise ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")\n262: \n263:     @staticmethod\n264:     def _validate_java_workspace(workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n265:         pom_file = workspace_path / \"pom.xml\"\n266:         if not pom_file.exists():\n267:             raise ValueError(\"No pom.xml found in workspace\")\n268: ```\n269: \n270: ### MetadataOptions 增强\n271: \n272: ```python\n273: # agentcube/models/pack_models.py\n274: from dataclasses import dataclass\n275: from typing import Optional, Dict, Any\n276: \n277: @dataclass\n278: class MetadataOptions:\n279:     agent_name: Optional[str] = None\n280:     language: Optional[str] = \"python\"\n281:     entrypoint: Optional[str] = None\n282:     port: Optional[int] = 8080\n283:     build_mode: Optional[str] = \"local\"\n284:     description: Optional[str] = None\n285:     requirements_file: Optional[str] = None\n286:     output: Optional[str] = None\n287:     verbose: bool = False\n288:     workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = \"\"\n289:     router_url: Optional[str] = \"\"\n290:     readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = \"\"\n291:     readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = 8080\n292:     registry_url: Optional[str] = \"\"\n293:     registry_username: Optional[str] = \"\"\n294:     registry_password: Optional[str] = \"\"\n295:     agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = \"\"\n296: \n297:     @classmethod\n298:     def from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> \"MetadataOptions\":\n299:         \"\"\"Create MetadataOptions from CLI options dictionary.\"\"\"\n300:         valid_fields = {f.name for f in cls.__dataclass_fields__.values()}\n301:         filtered = {k: v for k, v in options.items() if k in valid_fields}\n302:         return cls(**filtered)\n303: ```\n304: \n305: ---\n306: \n307: ## Timeline Estimate\n308: \n309: | Phase | Effort |\n310: |-------|--------|\n311: | 模型迁移 | 1-2 hours |\n312: | MetadataService 增强 | 2 hours |\n313: | MetadataOptions 增强 | 1 hour |\n314: | 测试 | 2 hours |\n315: | **Total** | **6-7 hours** |\n316: \n317: ---\n318: \n319: ## Existing Implementation Status\n320: \n321: 当前实现位于:\n322: - `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` (139 lines) — AgentMetadata + MetadataService\n323: - `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` (27 lines) — MetadataOptions\n324: \n325: ### Current Gaps\n326: \n327: 1. **模型位置**: AgentMetadata 在 services 包而非 models 包\n328: 2. **缺少 update_metadata**: 设计中要求但未实现\n329: 3. **缺少验证方法**: _validate_python_workspace, _validate_java_workspace 未实现\n330: 4. **MetadataOptions**: 缺少 from_options 类方法\n331: 5. **save_metadata**: 未使用 exclude_none=True\n\n(End of file - total 331 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型增强\n\n## Summary\n\n增强 MetadataService 和数据模型，实现完整的元数据生命周期管理和验证功能。\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\n`AgentMetadata` 和 `MetadataService` 是 CLI 核心的元数据管理组件。当前实现存在以下问题:\n1. `AgentMetadata` 位于 `services` 包，而非 `models` 包\n2. 缺少 `update_metadata` 方法\n3. 缺少语言特定的工作区验证\n4. `MetadataOptions` 缺少 `from_options` 类方法\n\n### Goal\n\n1. 迁移 AgentMetadata 到 models 包统一管理\n2. 实现完整的 MetadataService CRUD 操作","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775866617291,"end":1775866617298}}}}
