{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775866669046,"sessionID":"ses_2861a5243ffeYwG9du5NinetXQ","part":{"id":"prt_d79e67bb9001VDjqRJm1RDwBgd","messageID":"msg_d79e664fd001ZfbZPRPi4F4A7o","sessionID":"ses_2861a5243ffeYwG9du5NinetXQ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_46db12b8c9614d859b233afa","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-026: K8s/AgentCube Provider\n\n## Summary\n\n实现 CLI 的双 Provider 部署能力，支持将 Agent 部署到标准 Kubernetes (Deployment + Service) 或 AgentCube AgentRuntime CRD。\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nCLI 需要支持多目标部署平台:\n1. **标准 Kubernetes**: 使用原生 Deployment + Service 资源\n2. **AgentCube Platform**: 使用 AgentRuntime CRD (自定义资源)\n\n当前 `KubernetesProvider` 和 `AgentCubeProvider` 已实现基础功能,但与 `cli-toolkit/spec.md` 中的需求存在差距。\n\n### Goal\n\n1. 完善 AgentRuntime CRD 部署逻辑,符合规范要求\n2. 增强 Provider 错误处理和状态检测\n3. 确保 `publish` 和 `status` 命令正确路由到对应 Provider\n\n### Value\n\n- **多平台支持**: 同一 CLI 支持 K8s 和 AgentCube 两种部署目标\n- **一致性**: 统一的 Provider 接口抽象\n- **可观测性**: 完整的状态查询能力\n\n---\n\n## Scope\n\n### In-Scope\n\n| Component | Path | Description |\n|-----------|------|-------------|\n| AgentCubeProvider | `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | AgentRuntime CRD 部署 |\n| KubernetesProvider | `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | K8s Deployment/Service |\n| PublishRuntime | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | publish 命令编排 |\n| StatusRuntime | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | status 命令编排 |\n| Unit tests | `tests/test_k8s_provider.py` 等 | 测试覆盖 |\n\n### Out-of-Scope\n\n- CLI 参数变更 (已有 `--provider` 支持)\n- Python SDK 修改\n- client-go 代码生成\n\n---\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Purpose | Status |\n|------------|---------|--------|\n| `kubernetes>=28.0.0` | K8s API 调用 | Optional dep |\n| `pydantic>=2.0.0` | 数据验证 | Existing |\n| `pyyaml>=6.0` | YAML 序列化 | Existing |\n\n### Upstream\n\n- `cli-toolkit/design.md` — Provider 设计\n- `cli-toolkit/spec.md` — 部署需求\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n\n1. **CLI 用户** — 通过 `kubectl-agentcube publish --provider=agentcube|k8s`\n2. **CI/CD 流水线** — 自动化部署\n\n### Risks\n\n| Risk | Severity | Mitigation |\n|------|----------|------------|\n| K8s 库未安装 | Low | 优雅降级到 mock 模式 |\n| CRD 未安装 | Medium | 错误提示明确 |\n| 网络超时 | Medium | 配置超时参数 |\n\n---\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### Option 1: 仅支持 K8s Deployment (Not Selected)\n\n不实现 AgentRuntime CRD 支持,仅使用原生 K8s 资源。\n\n**Cons**:\n- 不符合 AgentCube 平台需求\n- 无法使用 AgentCube 特有功能 (session 管理)\n\n### Option 2: 仅支持 AgentCube CRD (Not Selected)\n\n仅通过 AgentRuntime CRD 部署。\n\n**Cons**:\n- 需要 AgentCube CRD 预先安装\n- 灵活性不足\n\n### Option 3: 双 Provider 支持 (Selected)\n\n同时支持 KubernetesProvider 和 AgentCubeProvider,通过 `--provider` 参数选择。\n\n**Pros**:\n- 灵活性高\n- 兼容多种部署场景\n- 符合设计规范\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n### Phase 1: AgentCubeProvider 增强\n\n- [ ] 添加 `imagePullSecrets` 支持 (默认 `default-secret`)\n- [ ] 确保 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` / `ROUTER_URL` 在 env_vars 中\n- [ ] 添加 `delete_agent_runtime` 方法\n\n### Phase 2: Status 增强\n\n- [ ] 完善 `_get_cr_k8s_status` 状态解析\n- [ ] 处理 CR 存在但无 status 的情况\n- [ ] 添加单元测试覆盖\n\n### Phase 3: 错误处理\n\n- [ ] 统一 Provider 异常类型\n- [ ] 添加超时配置支持\n- [ ] 完善日志输出\n\n### Phase 4: 测试\n\n- [ ] 补充 AgentCubeProvider 单元测试\n- [ ] 集成测试 publish/status 流程\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n### AgentCubeProvider\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| AC-001 | deploy_agent_runtime | 创建 AgentRuntime CR |\n| AC-002 | imagePullSecrets | 默认包含 `default-secret` |\n| AC-003 | get_agent_runtime | 正确获取 CR 状态 |\n| AC-004 | 环境变量注入 | WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL 自动注入 |\n\n### KubernetesProvider\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| K8S-001 | deploy_agent | 创建 Deployment + Service |\n| K8S-002 | node_port | 正确设置 NodePort 范围 |\n| K8S-003 | wait_for_deployment_ready | 超时抛出 TimeoutError |\n| K8S-004 | delete_agent | 清理 Deployment 和 Service |\n\n### Publish Command\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| PUB-001 | provider=agentcube | 调用 AgentCubeProvider |\n| PUB-002 | provider=k8s | 调用 KubernetesProvider |\n| PUB-003 | 缺少 router_url | 抛出 ValueError |\n\n### Status Command\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| STA-001 | agentcube provider | 返回 CR 状态 |\n| STA-002 | k8s provider | 返回 Deployment 状态 |\n| STA-003 | not_published | 返回提示信息 |\n\n---\n\n## Technical Design\n\n### AgentCubeProvider 增强\n\n```python\n# agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py\nclass AgentCubeProvider:\n    def deploy_agent_runtime(\n        self,\n        agent_name: str,\n        image_url: str,\n        port: int,\n        entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n        env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n        workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n        router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n        readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None,\n        readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None,\n    ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        # 1. 准备环境变量\n        final_env_vars = env_vars or {}\n        if workload_manager_url and \"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\" not in final_env_vars:\n            final_env_vars[\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\"] = workload_manager_url\n        if router_url and \"ROUTER_URL\" not in final_env_vars:\n            final_env_vars[\"ROUTER_URL\"] = router_url\n        \n        # 2. 构建 AgentRuntime spec\n        agent_runtime = {\n            \"apiVersion\": f\"{self.CR_GROUP}/{self.CR_VERSION}\",\n            \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n            \"metadata\": {\n                \"name\": agent_name,\n                \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n            },\n            \"spec\": {\n                \"maxSessionDuration\": \"8h\",\n                \"sessionTimeout\": \"15m\",\n                \"imagePullSecrets\": [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}],\n                # ... 其他字段\n            },\n        }\n```\n\n### Status 状态解析\n\n```python\n# agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py\ndef _get_cr_k8s_status(self, metadata: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    # 处理多种状态:\n    # - status.phase 存在 -> 返回 phase\n    # - CR 存在但无 status -> \"created_no_status\"\n    # - CR 不存在 -> \"not_found\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Timeline Estimate\n\n| Phase | Effort |\n|-------|--------|\n| AgentCubeProvider 增强 | 2 hours |\n| Status 增强 | 1 hour |\n| 错误处理 | 1 hour |\n| 测试 | 2 hours |\n| **Total** | **6 hours** |\n\n---\n\n## Existing Implementation Status\n\n当前实现位于:\n- `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` (296 行) — K8s 部署\n- `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` (218 行) — AgentRuntime 部署\n- `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` (321 行) — 发布编排\n- `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` (151 行) — 状态查询\n\n### Current Gaps\n\n1. **AgentCubeProvider**: 缺少 `imagePullSecrets` 配置\n2. **AgentCubeProvider**: 环境变量注入逻辑不完整\n3. **AgentCubeProvider**: 缺少 `delete_agent_runtime` 方法\n4. **StatusRuntime**: CR 状态解析需完善\n5. **测试覆盖**: AgentCubeProvider 单元测试不足","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775866669010,"end":1775866669043}}}}
